Seeker of Enlightenment				KEY:Spiritualist Archetype ~ Seeker of Enlightenment								CATEGORY:Archetype			TYPE:Archetype.SpiritualistArchetype																PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Seeker of Enlightenment],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Spiritualist_Archetype_SharedConsciousness=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_DetectUndead=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_CalmSpirit=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness=True,Spiritualist_Archetype_CallSpirit=True]						DESC:Sometimes a spiritualist is so haunted by a past life's failure to reach enlightenment that the past life is reborn not as a new creature but as a phantom in a spiritualist's consciousness. The spiritualist and phantom work in tandem to reach enlightenment and atone for the past life's failures.																																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Echoes of Expertise|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=1		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Words of the Past|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=5		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Karmic Insight|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=7	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Pinpoint Influence|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Echoes of Mastery|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=10	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Knowledge of the Ancestors|PRECLASS:1,Spiritualist=16																																									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.22																FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_SharedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_DetectUndead|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_CalmSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_FusedConsciousness|true		FACT:Spiritualist_Archetype_CallSpirit|true		FACT:Spiritualist_CF_SharedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_DetectUndead|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_CalmSpirit|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_SeeInvisibility|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_FusedConsciousness|true	FACT:Spiritualist_CF_CallSpirit|true

Echoes of Expertise					KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Echoes of Expertise									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																							DEFINE:ExpertiseEchoesBonus|0						DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Anger|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Dedication|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Despair|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Fear|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Hatred|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Jealousy|0	DEFINE:PhantomEmotionalFocus_Zeal|0				DESC:A seeker of enlightenment gains a +%1 bonus on checks attempted with the two skills determined by her phantom's emotional focus. When the phantom is confined to the seeker of enlightenment's consciousness, it grants a +%2 bonus on saving throws against mind-affecting effects. Once per day as a free action, the seeker of enlightenment can attempt a check with any Knowledge skill, including one in which she is not trained, and add %1 on the check.|SpiritualistLvl|ExpertiseEchoesBonus																																																																																																																																																																	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Seeker Emotional Focus|1																																					BONUS:VAR|ExpertiseEchoesBonus|2	BONUS:VAR|ExpertiseEchoesBonus|2|PREVARGTEQ:SpiritualistLvl,12																															SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Words of the Past					KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Words of the Past										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																													DESC:A seeker of enlightenment's connection with her past lives becomes so strong that she can cast comprehend languages at will as a spell-like ability, with a caster level equal to her spiritualist level.																																																																																																																																SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=SpiritualistLvl|Comprehend Languages																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Karmic Insight						KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Karmic Insight										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																				DEFINE:KarmicInsightTimes|0			DESC:A seeker of enlightenment gains the ability to understand which actions will push her toward ultimate understanding. She can cast augury as a spell-like ability %1 time(s) per day.|KarmicInsightTimes																																																																																																																																SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=KarmicInsightTimes|CASTERLEVEL=SpiritualistLvl|Augury																																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|KarmicInsightTimes|min((SpiritualistLvl-3)/4,4)																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Pinpoint Influence					KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Pinpoint Influence									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																													DESC:A seeker of enlightenment gains the ability to track objects that are important to her goal of enlightenment. She can cast locate object as a spell-like ability once per day, with a duration of 10 minutes.																																																																																																																															SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=10|Locate Object																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Echoes of Mastery					KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Echoes of Mastery										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																												DESC:A seeker of enlightenment gains the bonus on saving throws from echoes of expertise even when her phantom is manifested. Additionally, once per day, she can take 20 on any Knowledge check, including one in which she is not trained.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Knowledge of the Ancestors			KEY:Seeker of Enlightenment ~ Knowledge of the Ancestors							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpiritualistClassFeatures.SeekerOfEnlightenmentClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																													DESC:A seeker of enlightenment learns how to tap into the knowledge of her past lives. She can cast legend lore as a spell-like ability once per day.																																																																																																																																														SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=SpiritualistLvl|Legend Lore																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.23


