Superiority							KEY:Psychic Discipline ~ Superiority												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Psychic Discipline.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																										DESC:You know that you are far better than average creatures of your kind. The more you leverage your psychic talents to prove yourself superior, the more powerful you become.																																																																																																																																								ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psychic Discipline Superiority ~ Bonus Spells|Psychic Discipline Superiority ~ Self-Assurance|PRECLASS:1,Psychic=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psychic Discipline Superiority ~ At Arm's Length|PRECLASS:1,Psychic=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psychic Discipline Superiority ~ Magical Hoarder|PRECLASS:1,Psychic=13																																															BONUS:VAR|PhrenicPoolAbility|CHA

